#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:580
msgid ""
"Vouch messages you wrote were redacted. Governance votes you cast were kept "
"as-is — a vote is a community record, not personal data, and removing it "
"would silently change a settled decision."
msgstr ""
"あなたが書いた推薦メッセージは編集されました。あなたが行ったガバナンス投票はそのまま保持されました。投票はコミュニティの記録であり、個人データではなく、削除すると確定した決定が黙って変更されてしまうためです。"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:623
msgid ""
"Past newsletter delivery records were anonymized; per-issue delivery counts "
"were kept for statistics."
msgstr "過去のニュースレター配信記録は匿名化されました。各号ごとの配信数は統計のため保持されています。"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:690
msgid ""
"Agnosis is a federated art-publishing plugin. The following is a starting "
"point for describing what it collects — review and adapt it to your site's "
"actual configuration before publishing."
msgstr ""
"Agnosis "
"は、アーティスト向けの分散型アート出版プラグインです。以下は、収集する内容を説明するための出発点です。公開する前に、このサイトの実際の設定に合わせて確認し、調整してください。"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:691
msgid "What personal data we collect and why"
msgstr "収集する個人データとその理由"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:692
msgid ""
"When you apply to join, we store your email address, display name, biography,"
" statement, and portfolio link to run the community vouching process. When "
"you email us artwork, a biography, or an event, the content of that email "
"(including your address) is stored while it is processed and reviewed. When "
"you subscribe to our newsletter or message an artist through their contact "
"form, we store your email address (and, for contact messages, your IP "
"address) to deliver that message or send you future issues."
msgstr ""
"参加申請を行うと、コミュニティの推薦プロセスを実施するために、メールアドレス、表示名、経歴、ステートメント、ポートフォリオリンクを保存します。アート作品、経歴、イベントをメールで送信すると、そのメールの内容（あなたのアドレスを含む）は、処理および審査中に保存されます。ニュースレターを購読する場合や、連絡フォームからアーティストにメッセージを送る場合は、そのメッセージを配信したり将来の号を送信したりするために、メールアドレス（連絡メッセージの場合はIPアドレスも）を保存します。"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:693
msgid "Who we share it with"
msgstr "共有先"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:694
msgid ""
"Submitted artwork descriptions and images may be sent to a third-party AI "
"provider (OpenAI or Anthropic, depending on this site's configuration) to "
"help write publication text and enhance images. If this site instead uses "
"WordPress's own built-in AI Client (configured under Settings → Connectors), "
"submitted content is sent to whichever AI service that connector points to "
"instead. Approved posts are also broadcast publicly over ActivityPub (the "
"Fediverse) as part of this plugin's core federation feature."
msgstr ""
"Submitted artwork descriptions and images may be sent to a third-party AI "
"provider (OpenAI or Anthropic, depending on this site's configuration) to "
"help write publication text and enhance images. If this site instead uses "
"WordPress's own built-in AI Client (configured under Settings → Connectors), "
"submitted content is sent to whichever AI service that connector points to "
"instead. Approved posts are also broadcast publicly over ActivityPub (the "
"Fediverse) as part of this plugin's core federation feature."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:695
msgid "How long we retain your data"
msgstr "データの保持期間"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:696
msgid ""
"Retention varies by data type; see this site's administrator for specifics. "
"You can request a copy of, or the erasure of, the personal data described "
"above at any time using this site's standard WordPress data request tools."
msgstr ""
"保持期間はデータの種類によって異なります。詳細はこのサイトの管理者にお問い合わせください。上記の個人データのコピーや削除は、このサイトの標準的な "
"WordPress のデータ要求ツールを使って、いつでも依頼できます。"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:724
msgid ""
"Submitted text and images may be processed by a third-party AI provider. "
"Approved posts are published publicly and shared across the Fediverse — this "
"cannot be fully undone later."
msgstr ""
"送信されたテキストと画像は、第三者のAIプロバイダーによって処理される場合があります。承認された投稿は公開され、Fediverse "
"全体で共有されます。これは後から完全に取り消すことはできません。"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:725
